## Domain -> Audit trail (unified review comments + build runs)

**Context**: Status-change comments lived only inside the per-version Validation timeline and the
build-run history lived in its own Runs page. Users wanted a single domain-wide activity feed that
interleaves both: every status switch (with its comment) and every build run + result.

**Changes**:
1. `src/back/objects/domain/Domain.py` — added `audit_trail_result(svc, *, limit)`: merges the
   review/validation event log (`list_review_events`, all versions) with the build-run history
